# <%= projectName %>

## Prerequisites

- Go <%= toolchain.go %>+
- golangci-lint
- pre-commit
- gitleaks
- staticcheck, deadcode, govulncheck, goimports, and go-mutesting for the full quality gate

## Setup

```bash
go mod tidy
pre-commit install
make check
```

## Development

| Command | Description |
| --- | --- |
| `make lint` | Run golangci-lint and custom anvil analyzers |
| `make test` | Run Go tests |
| `make check` | Run tier 1 and tier 2 validation |
| `make quality` | Run all validation, including mutation testing |
| `make fix` | Auto-format Go source files |

## Project Structure

```text
cmd/app/         Application entrypoint
internal/seed/   Example package and tests
tools/           Tool tracking and custom analyzers
```
